\hAddress submitted to system CFG bus for read \nThe address stored here is used as the address to request a read on the system CFG bus. This is for the Sequencer, with its 16-bit address space, to access system CFG bus, which has 32-bit address space.

\hAddress submitted to system CFG bus for read \nThe address stored here is used as the address to request a write on the system CFG bus. This is for the 16-bit address space sequencer to access system CFG bus which has 32-bit address space. Note that t

\hCFG bus request read data, upper 16-bit \nReading this word extracts data from the Read FIFO. When the Read FIFO is empty, reading this word will return undefined value. Data is extracted lowest-addressed-word first.

\hCFG bus request read data, lower 16-bit \nReading this word extracts data from the Read FIFO. When the Read FIFO is empty, reading this word will return undefined value. Data is extracted lowest-addressed-word first.
\hCFG bus request write data \nWriting to this register fills the Write FIFO. When the Write FIFO is full, subsequent writes will be ignored.
